Why Choose Wooden Crates for Shipping & Storage?

Not all packaging is created equal. Standard boxes and plastic containers simply don’t provide the structural integrity needed for heavy, irregular, or fragile loads. Here’s why wood crates are such a smart choice:

Superior Strength: Wood crates offer heavy-duty protection against impact, crushing, and external stress.

Custom Fit: Every crate is built to your exact specifications—no wasted space, no over-packing.

Versatile: Suitable for air, sea, and ground transportation, as well as long-term storage.

Affordable: Wood crates balance cost with protection better than many alternative materials.

Eco-Friendly: Made from sustainable wood, crates are recyclable and reusable for future shipments.

These benefits make wood crates the preferred solution for businesses serious about safeguarding their goods.

Expertly Crafted Crates Built for What You Ship

At Crates of Las Vegas, we don’t just build crates—we engineer solutions. Our fully customizable approach ensures that your wood crate is precisely what your product needs, considering weight, size, fragility, and destination handling conditions.

Our wood crate service includes:

Custom Wooden Crates: Tailored sizes to secure any product—from small parts to oversized equipment.

Heavy-Duty Crates: Reinforced boards and beams that withstand intensive handling.

Slatted & Vented Crates: Ideal for items requiring airflow or visibility without sacrificing protection.

Fully Enclosed Crates: Maximum security for sensitive or fragile goods.

Stackable Designs: Optimized for storage efficiency and transport stacking requirements.

Each crate is built using premium wood materials and craftsmanship standards that ensure structural integrity through every stage of handling and shipping.

