Custom Crates Engineered for Compliance & Logistics

International and domestic shipments often come with strict packaging requirements. Wooden crates can be engineered to meet specific industry standards, including:

ISPM-15 Heat Treatment for international export compliance

Reinforced Structural Frames for heavy industrial cargo

Padding & Protection Systems to guard fragile components

Crates of Las Vegas works with clients to design packaging that meets regulatory requirements while maximizing protection and minimizing freight costs.

